headline: Keurig Dr Pepper to Report First Quarter 2025 Results and Host Conference Call
summary: Keurig Dr Pepper Inc. (NASDAQ: KDP) will release its financial results for the first quarter ended March 31, 2025 before the market opens on Thursday, April 24, 2025. The Company will also hold a conference call on Thursday, April 24, 2025 at 7:30 AM (ET) to discuss the results, which will be hosted by Tim Cofer, Chief Executive Officer, and Sudhanshu Priyadarshi, Chief Financial Officer and President, International.
